Well my last journal entry had mentioned that I had seen Bubba that weekend before. Just reading that kind of upsets me knowing the last journal entry I wrote in a while had mentioned the one person we all have recently lost. Its like I find myself fighting to hide the missing feelings for him. i just dont know how to cope missing such a caring, fun loving, life of the party guy. Who has been my friend for so many years. Its just still unbelievable that he is the one who is gone. i guess all i can really say is i miss him alot. 

Well I guess I could update my journal on some of  the things that has been going on in my life. A month and a half ago I had gone out with a kid named Theo. Who is still around in my life which is the sucky thing because I see him all the time he works with me. Well I am now going out with an amazing guy Scott who at first I really could say I didnt care about at all. He was just a rebound from when Theo and I broke up, but he has grown on me now. At first I could say i would of broken up with Scott to be with Theo again if it was possible, but it has changed now im not even sure what i would do i would probably just stay with scott. I mean I cant say that i still dont miss the thought of how me and Theo were, but just seeing him sometimes and just looking at him kind of upsets me. I start to think well i wonder how being with him right now and that much longer down the road how it would of turned out if I wouldnt have fucked up. Would we stay together? or would we still have broken up? I guess i will never know. 

Life: What to actually say about that subject who knows anymore. What is it actually holding for you? Is it just to create you a lesson before you meet the big man or is it meaningless  you find out in the end. I know im rambling, but I feel like i have so much to get off my chest and by rambling maybe ill come up with one of the things to get off my chest. Works getting hectic since everybody is going off to school and I am picking up more hours We only have 2 managers left and everybody is suspecting dave picking up and leaving after his wedding in september but who knows? Jimmy just got back from his vacation and I have been planning on asking him for a raise, but I think i need to bust my ass for a little bit before I ask him. School: I havent spoken to my father in a while I dont know if he has been getting my emails at all he is supposed to be sending me money for a car so I can have a way of getting to school and back. Thats why I will be going back and starting classes in the spring. My 19th birthday is a month away pretty much which is pretty awesome since it is on a Friday this year. Well enough with all my rambling  I just thought I would post since I havent posted in a while.

Well come to find out ive done something wrong this weekend and I cant tend to find what I really did wrong. People are hating me for all the wrong reasons and I seriously would like to be filled in, but thats kind of hard knowing these people wont speak to me. I am hoping we will be able to work things out and sit down and talk about things, but it doesnt look like thats going to happen. Whatever they think i did I guess i will say sorry  for one person said i was talking shit about her when thats totally not true when her name didnt even come out of my mouth once and if it did it wasnt in a bad way at all. The other says I have going on things that i have "heard" which I really dont understand whats going on.It upsets me that they wont even listen to me, tell me what I have done wrong, and hear what I have to say about it, but i guess I cant really change anything about there choices. I guess I might be experiencing my father alone instead with the one person i wanted to share the experience with and the one person I wanted to be there with me. 

Well lets just say this weekend was quite the blur. Friday night went to Matt's house saw Bubba after the longest time, and met some of the unknown people Chrissy talks about. I found myself getting totally fucked up after 1 xanny and a crap load of beer. Hanging out with some of the older brothers friends and having them yell "Little Thiess" all night. 

Saturday night found myself getting wsted at 6. At Alli's like usual for Alli's 18th birthday party kind f thing. It was supposed to be a surprise but she ended up finding out  about it. So i was wasted at 8 probably even before that. Saw Jeremy Kubiak which was quite a surprise knowing i was so wasted i saw him and ducked in the other room. At the end of our little fiasco i ended up being nice and saying hi. Played flip cup for the first time which got me wasted fast and then some games of Beer pong screwed me over. Chrissy and I ended up leaving from Alli's at 10 and decided to go to Oyster Pub to meet up with Shane for his birthday shit. Saw Jonny, Jmac, and Tony there ate some food. Ended up hanging out with Shane, Boswell, Brett, Walker, Jim, and the rest of the group for the rest of the night at Oyster Pub until 2 decided to go to Frank's and that was boring so we thought the club was going to be boring but knowing that chrissy's Brandon was inside the whole time bummed her out the next day. Left at 2 and got home by 3 passed out. The next day woke up at 10 went to the mall, ate, and then came home. That was my interesting weekend even though there is more to it in details anyway but no need to worry about that. 

Well I guess ill be on my own or feel that way for a while. i really dont know what I do or what i did but im really sorry for whatever you think i have done. 
im out.

I do understand if I do write something in here offensive or something that bothers you please dont take it personal its just how I feel and  what goes through my mind. Certain people in my life are doing certain things I dont approve of, but all I can do is sit back and watch them do it. It all comes down to 1 thing. coke. Ive seen people do it, Ive heard about people doing it, and ive talked about people doing it. I never realized how bad the drug can be and how it can bother me until I realized even my closest most favorite people in the world have experienced it or are doing it. I feel like im the outcast becuase I havent done it and I dont want to do it. I am also scared im going to be suckered into it or im going to see one of the people I love do it and im just going to crack and fall and thats going to be the end. Finding out made me upset and crazy ripping things off my walls taking pictures out of frames and just laying on my bed room floor pounding it and crying histerically. Becuase you always thought that those people who were so close to you wouldnt do something like that and it just stuns you. I was just hoping that I was going to wake up in my bed and it was all going to be just a bad dream, but it wasnt. Thinking that the person you know who always told you that they were going to prove everyone wrong and not do it was amazing to hear that they actually did. People I have met that I know have done it before doesnt upset as much as someone I have known for many years that say they are never going to do it and they actually end up doing it just is disappointing. I feel like in the circle of my closest friends im being shut out and im about to be pushed out just because i dont do it. i feel like i just need to get out of this town and get away for a little bit and the trip to Costa in 24 days will do that for me. Just being in paradise will be the best thing i will need. Certain people wh influence and sit there and let and watch people do it like shawn Carpenter sickens me. Hes just a complete piece of shit. That drug ruined his life and made him into the piece of shit he is today only caring about himself and his feelings not caring at all about anybody else but him self. Just worrying about who can get him drugs and fucked up. Thats what he calls his friends. Just the drug makes you into  totally different person than you were before it alters your beliefs and actions of your everyday life. i just feel like I cant do anything about it and im just stuck in the pit and nobody is coming to get me and im trying to claw myself out. 

Well this weekend was nuts not so much Friday, but Saturday was. Jill came and picked me up went to Al's. Took 2 Shots of vodka, drank out of Al's Malibu and popped a Xan. Went to Joeys all fucked up and drank more beer from the keg. Ended up taking a couple keg stands. Then dont remember shit walked out of the garage threw up in the street, on my shoe, and on my purse that pretty much sucked.  Sat in the curb for a few minutes than wanted to walk. Dont remember the walk but ended up at US 1 and Wilmette seeing cop cars and a flipped truck. It was Ph il's truck that was flipped and all the cops knew I was wasted. So a cop named Jay who comes into Hull's knew I wasted and gave me a ride home. So I ended up at home safe. Then Sunday was a definite 360. What a crazy time i am just glad its kind of over.

i find my self confused about many things. i dont know whats going on with things lately but things have been affecting me alot more. Little things are getting to me I mean i dont know if  its just me or if they should be getting  to me or not. I find myself going between 2 things i mean one part of the day I feel really upset about everything and the other part of the day im just in the middle about everything. It feels like my friends are drifting apart from me or it may just be me thinking that. i need something just to make me happy all the time maybe find some xannies this weekend or some other kind of fucking pill. I dont know what to do about the whole Kaytee situation. It seems everytime she makes up with me she goes and turns around and does something else that just pisses me off. First its not being around and not really being there anymore. Then its She blows us off after making plans with us. Then she picks out my flaws on multiple occasions to find out im getting pissed and then says shes kidding, but I dont like someone who is going to sit there and humiliate me all the time in front of all my friends with certain things that are tempermental to me i just dont know i guess it could be with draw from drugs but i dont think so i dont think it could make me feel the way i do feel but then again drugs do crazy things.

Well ended up asking my mom if i could drink some champagne becuase i was going to be able to deal with that woman all night sober and the only illegal my mom will let me do in front of her on holidays is drink. So of course i suck down my first to glasses until I get 9 r 10 really didnt keep track. i call up Mauri she comes picks me up with Kaytee and Ashley falling. i was drunk off my ass. We took a trip to the park where Shea Miller was i said hi to him and I guess reintroduced my self even tho he already knew who I was since we did go out. Headed to Kaytee's sat out front smoked some. Then ended up ordering pizza the pizza guy showed up and i had fallen asleep on this mat thing out side the house. that I didnt even eat everyone else did i was so pissed becuase while they are eating pizza my head is in a toilet puking not fun at all.  Then ended up passing out on Kaytee's bed after she helped take care of me. Oh one other thing Kaytee and Mauri pinned me down again and did some marker fun EASTER = DRUNK!! Well ill update the rest later leaving the library when im supposed to be at school I am a failure and suck at life.

Well he told me he couldnt reschedule it again so he would have to give me 2 days of ISS. Well then i hear over the walkie talkies ms. Jones is asking to see me. Well i go back to ms. Well then she put me in ISS or the rest of yesterday and I had to go all today and ill be in there again  tomorrow. 

Let me say life is pretty much boring for me right now. oh  and i decided FUCK BOYS!!!!! i am so sick of them all I ever do is fucking be nice and  of course I get a fucking asshole back. My life is now school work and more school and work. i am also probably failing Spanish and English but hey what can you do I havent been to Spanish in god knows how long. i hate Seabreeze so much i wish I could just drop out and go to DBCC. i really do wish i could just straighten up and actually get my act together and go to school and actually do my work but its way too hard I just cant do it. Well I guess tomorrow is another day of ISS which should be fun  cant wait!!! Well the good thing about tomorrow is Mauri and I are both off. Well i guess peace out homie!

Well the kid asked for me back. then a week later he fucks up and needs some place to stay so he stays at my place for a couple of days and then we get into a huge fight break up and he goes and stays with someone else. i dont even kno what to think anymore. Seriously i miss him soo much but then at the same time i dont want a boyfriend to deal with right now. i feel so stupid for saying that becuase i finally get what i want and then I dont want it anymore. its quite stupid.. i havent updated in a while i dont know I either dont have the time to or dont feel the need to. i feel empty without him and i feel the need  to have him around but when he is around i feel smothered with his presence. i guess i just dont kno what to think anymore. Well we go back to school Monday which i am definitly not looking forward to. i seriously hate that place. My grades suck i never want to go or do any work. i have no motivation and it just feels like i have failed myself and my mom. I guess im just going to have to face the consequences whatever those might be. I dont know how to act or sometimes i dont know what path to choose or what choices to make I just feel like each step i take im fucking up my life even more. late.

Is it normal to think that life has no meaning? That all your here for  is to learn a lesson. i feel that way sometimes that god puts these difficult paths through your life to make you stronger  so when you end up in heaven you are a stronger person than you once were. i feel like everything I count on to work out or happen always crumbles to pieces or just doesnt ever go the way i want it to. i have learned that even your closest friends can betray you, but you still forgive them becuase you feel a emptiness without them. I have also learned that people you care about the most always lie even if you dont want them to. Sometimes I feel so stupid for succeeding with some of my actions that it was all a waste of time or should of never happen. Its funny how someone can tell you that they care for you so much and only wants you and nobody else and then turns around and acts like thats not even how  they felt. I am  to the point I am sick of my life.
He is finally back and it almost feels wonderful he got home yesterday and I see him tomorrow thats the only thing thats missing right now. I cant wait.
